NAME
       
Text::Original - Find original, non-quoted text in a message

SYNOPSIS
           
	use Text::Original;
	my $sentence = first_sentence($email->body);

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

